@SampleMinimalApiNoAot_HostAddress = http://localhost:5157

### =============================================================================
### Non-AOT Example: Reflection-based Value Object Validation
### =============================================================================
### This example uses the reflection fallback path (no Asp.Generator).
### The behavior is identical to the AOT approach.

### =============================================================================
### Register User - Valid Request
### =============================================================================
POST {{SampleMinimalApiNoAot_HostAddress}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "John",
    "lastName": "Doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "secreT!123"
}

### =============================================================================
### Register User - Invalid (empty fields)
### =============================================================================
### Demonstrates automatic validation with reflection-based converters
POST {{SampleMinimalApiNoAot_HostAddress}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "",
    "lastName": "",
    "email": "invalid-email",
    "password": "test"
}

### =============================================================================
### Name Validation - Property Names Preserved
### =============================================================================
### Both fname and lname use the same Name type.
### Error messages correctly identify each property.
POST {{SampleMinimalApiNoAot_HostAddress}}/names/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "fname": "",
    "lname": ""
}

### Expected response (400 Bad Request):
### {
###     "errors": {
###         "fname": ["Name cannot be empty."],
###         "lname": ["Name cannot be empty."]
###     }
### }

### =============================================================================
### Name Validation - Valid
### =============================================================================
POST {{SampleMinimalApiNoAot_HostAddress}}/names/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "fname": "John",
    "lname": "Doe"
}

### =============================================================================
### Manual Validation (for comparison)
### =============================================================================
POST {{SampleMinimalApiNoAot_HostAddress}}/users/register-manual
